    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，开发占40%。那除了开发之外，还有哪些主要板块？测试、运维这些要不要单独列出来？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Testing & QA",
        "Infrastructure"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，测试和质量保证要单独算，大概15%。基础设施这块包括服务器和云服务，给12%。设计和用户体验也很重要，占10%。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Testing & QA",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Design & UX"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我现在加上这几个板块：开发40%、测试15%、基础设施12%、设计10%。项目管理这块怎么算？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Development",
        "Testing & QA",
        "Infrastructure",
        "Design & UX",
        "Project Management"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "项目管理给8%吧，还有市场推广7%。对了，法务合规这块不能漏，虽然占比小但必须有，5%左右。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Project Management",
